Daphne Maxwell Reid https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daphne_Maxwell_Reid 0 Daphne Etta Maxwell-Reid (born July 13, 1948) is an American actress and comedian. She is best known for her role as the second Vivian Banks on the NBC sitcom The Fresh Prince of Bel-Air from 1993 until 1996.
